    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "found his watch on the nightstand today. i just stared at it for an hour. it's like the world is still spinning and people are still doing things, but for me, everything just stopped. it doesn't feel like a \"new beginning\" or anything... it just feels like i'm waiting for something that isn't coming back. like i'm just stuck in this weird, empty waiting room.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
