      "content": "\"gently let go of the need to keep going\"... that sounds almost peaceful, in a way. but it's so hard to just \"exist\" when every part of me feels broken. i feel like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. does it ever feel like there's just no reason to fight it anymore? like, why bother trying to fix something that's already completely gone?",
